                Office of Global Engagement
              









International Affairs










The Office of Global Engagement's Director of International Affairs and Outreach oversees UIC’s international agreements, international relations, distinguished international visitors, international delegations, and the Diplomat in Residence program. The Director also advises UIC faculty on the Fulbright Scholar Program and is UIC’s chief liaison with the Chicago Consular Corps which includes all consular officials representing foreign governments in Chicago.





