          Heading link



 
Copy link












                            International Collaborations
                    

                Learn about developing international affiliations and discover UIC's current partners around the globe
            












                            Diplomat in Residence at UIC
                    

                Meet Susan Falatko, U.S. State Department Diplomat in Residence for the Midwest Region and former Deputy Chief of Mission at the U.S. Embassy in Ljubljana
            












                            Fulbright Programs
                    

                Explore a compilation of resources about the various Fulbright Programs offered to U.S. and non-U.S. scholars and researchers
            












                            Chicago Consular Corps
                    

                Read more about the Chicago Consular Corps, a group comprised of Consulates, Consulates General and Honorary Consulates based in Chicago that represent over 80 countries
            



















 
